  "texts": [
    "In secondary schools, researchers have also reported an increase in students' knowledge of AI algorithms (Yoder et al., 2020) and machine learning concepts (Sakulkueakulsuk et al., 2018), as well as their recognition of AI patterns (Wan et al., 2020).",
    "For example, students understood the fundamental neural networks of machine learning concepts by developing a classification model of recycling images (Martins et al., 2023).",
    "Affective and behavioral outcomes have been identified in AI learning tool studies within K-12 contexts.",
    "In general, students' motivation to learn AI (Han et al., 2018; Shamir & Levin, 2021, 2022) and their interest in the course (Mariescu-Istodor & Jormanainen, 2019; Martins et al., 2023) were enhanced as a result of AI learning activities.",
    "Students' perceptions of the relevance of AI to their life also increased (Kajiwara et al., 2023; Lin et al., 2021)."
  ],
